{"ts":"2026-07-06T21:09:23.206Z","author":"maintainer-agent","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"GitHub: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/issues/473\n\nFold a light verification pass into `pm install` output (activation status, registered commands/item types, health verdict) so agents skip the follow-up `pm package doctor` in the happy path. Builds on the multi-target install aggregation shipped for pm-hj9h (per-target success/failure rows)."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"pm-yjim"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"GH-473: pm install prints a post-install verification summary"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"Dogfood GH-473: after pm install <package>, agents must run pm package doctor to confirm the install worked; a brief inline verification summary saves an invocation. Duplicate check: searched post-install verification summary — pm-b3e9 covers PRE-install owning-package hints; no overlap."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Feature"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"open"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":3},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["agent-experience","gh-issue","packages","token-efficiency"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:09:23.206Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-06T21:09:23.206Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"maintainer-agent"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":90},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"pm install output ends with a verification summary (activation status, registered commands/types, health ok/degraded) equivalent to a light package-doctor pass; failures keep the existing per-target failure rows; covered by specs"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"pm-ugqx"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"low"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":"high"}],"before_